{"type":"message","id":"ff001efe","parentId":"ddefdd03","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:58:16.157Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_32t1b0zsfnfx_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"OpenClaw Feishu channel listen all messages without mention\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1538,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f8ed81d5d2075632\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f8ed81d5d2075632\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/feishu\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5a6cecf245d87f18\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5a6cecf245d87f18\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"737ead635a11037e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nopenclaw/docs/channels/feishu.md at main - GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"737ead635a11037e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/channels/feishu.md\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a4573b5db19dfaf6\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a4573b5db19dfaf6\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f62400e3603938ba\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu | OpenClaw Docs\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f62400e3603938ba\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclaw-ai.com/en/docs/channels/feishu/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"90b5524a95f0de49\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"90b5524a95f0de49\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclaw-ai.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"17f73ceb7ba6ea01\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu - OpenClaw - Open Source AI Assistant\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"17f73ceb7ba6ea01\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclawcn.com/en/docs/channels/feishu/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f85acd64366154df\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f85acd64366154df\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclawcn.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c620636a087d8fb4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSetting up your Feishu Bot with OpenClaw | OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c620636a087d8fb4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://open-claw.bot/docs/channels/feishu/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c392dfeb41c08209\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n4. Connect and Subscribe Now, tell Feishu to send messages via WebSocket. Run openclaw onboard or openclaw channels add in your terminal. Select Feishu and enter your credentials. Start the gateway with openclaw gateway. In the Feishu console under Event Subscription, choose Use long connection and add the im. message .receive_v1 event.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c392dfeb41c08209\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"open-claw.bot\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"OpenClaw Feishu channel listen all messages without mention","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":1538,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8ed81d5d2075632\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu - OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f8ed81d5d2075632\">>>","url":"https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/feishu","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5a6cecf245d87f18\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5a6cecf245d87f18\">>>","siteName":"docs.openclaw.ai"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"737ead635a11037e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nopenclaw/docs/channels/feishu.md at main - GitHub\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"737ead635a11037e\">>>","url":"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/channels/feishu.md","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a4573b5db19dfaf6\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a4573b5db19dfaf6\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f62400e3603938ba\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu | OpenClaw Docs\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f62400e3603938ba\">>>","url":"https://openclaw-ai.com/en/docs/channels/feishu/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"90b5524a95f0de49\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"90b5524a95f0de49\">>>","siteName":"openclaw-ai.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"17f73ceb7ba6ea01\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu - OpenClaw - Open Source AI Assistant\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"17f73ceb7ba6ea01\">>>","url":"https://openclawcn.com/en/docs/channels/feishu/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f85acd64366154df\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu /Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f85acd64366154df\">>>","siteName":"openclawcn.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c620636a087d8fb4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSetting up your Feishu Bot with OpenClaw | OpenClaw\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c620636a087d8fb4\">>>","url":"https://open-claw.bot/docs/channels/feishu/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c392dfeb41c08209\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n4. Connect and Subscribe Now, tell Feishu to send messages via WebSocket. Run openclaw onboard or openclaw channels add in your terminal. Select Feishu and enter your credentials. Start the gateway with openclaw gateway. In the Feishu console under Event Subscription, choose Use long connection and add the im. message .receive_v1 event.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"c392dfeb41c08209\">>>","siteName":"open-claw.bot"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774364296153}}
