{"type":"message","id":"c3736028","parentId":"f9fb2e2f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:58:52.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! I found something very useful. The last result from coloradmin.cn mentions:\n\n```\n模式 3按单个群精细化配置最灵活\n# 指定群必须 才回复\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groups.oc_群ID.requireMention true --strict-json\n# 指定群不用 也回复\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groups.oc_群ID.requireMention false --strict-json\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nThis seems to be the key! There's a `requireMention` setting that can be set to `false` for specific groups, allowing the bot to respond to all messages in that group without being @mentioned.\n\n\nLet me see if I can pull more details from that page to get the full picture.","thinkingSignature":"c8de7a7d4213e0fddb5bce0fe2929472b1f7677842c0d1de8b4e87293223e4f5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0dkvu6cd29qw_1","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"http://www.coloradmin.cn/o/2433211.html","maxChars":10000}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":13748,"output":201,"cacheRead":17422,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31371,"cost":{"input":0.004124399999999999,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00104532,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005410919999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774364323189,"responseId":"0611d9a30ffeda7c0ac0ca165b6650ed"}}
