{"type":"message","id":"f9923ba5","parentId":"842bd789","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:59:04.552Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6qhdl7709yl2_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"openclaw config set channels.feishu.groups requireMention false\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1495,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1143614ff4f45b99\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu - OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1143614ff4f45b99\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://docs.openclaw.ai/channels/feishu\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b5d4ef9d1e1698af\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu/Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b5d4ef9d1e1698af\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"docs.openclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1b3eab64f691c1db\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nopenclaw/docs/channels/feishu.md at main - GitHub\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1b3eab64f691c1db\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/channels/feishu.md\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e12ba715617a6500\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhen using webhook mode, set both channels.feishu.verificationToken and channels.feishu.encryptKey in your config . To get the values: In Feishu Open Platform, open your app Go to Development → Events & Callbacks (开发配置 → 事件与回调) Open the Encryption tab (加密策略) Copy Verification Token and Encrypt Key The screenshot below shows where to find the Verification Token. The ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e12ba715617a6500\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd3dea66326aa690\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw Configuration Guide — Complete Settings Reference\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd3dea66326aa690\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.getopenclaw.ai/docs/configuration\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"132049a2f1ed3028\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nComplete OpenClaw config .yaml reference. All settings explained: AI models, channels, multi-agent setup, plugins, secrets management, and more.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"132049a2f1ed3028\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.getopenclaw.ai\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2798fce12aa7b540\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu - OpenClaw - Open Source AI Assistant\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2798fce12aa7b540\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclawcn.com/en/docs/channels/feishu/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3abff92da301fb00\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu (Lark) is a team chat platform used by companies for messaging and collaboration. This plugin connects OpenClaw to a Feishu/Lark bot using the platform's WebSocket event subscription so messages can be received without exposing a public webhook URL.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3abff92da301fb00\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"openclawcn.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6560b406efef3489\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeishu | Docs | OpenClaw\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"6560b406efef3489\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://openclaws.io/docs/cha