{"type":"message","id":"d388e934","parentId":"4013bff9","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:59:25.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Almost everything is blocked. Based on the search results I did get, I can see the key finding:\n\nFrom the coloradmin.cn snippet:\n```\n模式 3按单个群精细化配置最灵活\n# 指定群必须 才回复\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groups.oc_群ID.requireMention true --strict-json\n# 指定群不用 也回复\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groups.oc_群ID.requireMention false --strict-json\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nAnd from the CSDN article snippet about routing rules:\n1. 显式 @ 优先 - @谁谁回复\n\n\n2. 昵称命中次优先 - 消息包含机器人昵称时也会触发回复\n\nSo the solution is setting `requireMention: false` on the specific group! This is exactly what the user wants. Let me try searching for more information about this feature.","thinkingSignature":"8cfe862a67b8ef4fffe89fbc9cc31eca377b721a3fb1e5de556afe98974f186d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1ds94veyhysh_1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"openclaw feishu requireMention 配置 群ID","count":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15836,"output":229,"cacheRead":17422,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33487,"cost":{"input":0.0047507999999999995,"output":0.0002748,"cacheRead":0.00104532,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00607092}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774364358926,"responseId":"0611d9c78851a6b9cdd073d92c12dd1b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8df763d","parentId":"d388e934","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:59:26.821Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1ds94veyhysh_1","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"openclaw feishu requireMention 配置 群ID\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1161,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd03c3922756d2c3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw 接入飞书 （2）- 群组、权限、多渠道 - 知乎\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bd03c3922756d2c3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013958294977394200\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bdb2566423dd37fc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n上一篇我们聊了 OpenClaw 接入飞书的基础部署流程，从装 CLI 到私聊跑通，顺利的话 20 分钟搞定。 建议先读一下： 《一条命令装好，几步配置跑通—— OpenClaw 飞书部署实战》 但私聊只是起点。真正要在团队里用起来，你一定会遇到这些问题： 怎么让机器人进群？进了群怎么控制谁能跟它说话？ 能不 ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bdb2566423dd37fc\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"zhuanlan.zhihu.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"87f147124cebbef5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw 飞书群消息配置：requireMention 详解 - SaiitaのBlog\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"87f147124cebbef5\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.saiita.com.cn/note/computer/ai/openclaw/openclaw-%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E7%BE%A4%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9Arequiremention-%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3.html\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fa9b928d2e85acee\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nrequireMention参数控制群聊中机器人是否需被@才回复：true（默认）时仅响应@消息，false时响应所有消息但会增加API调用量。该参数可在群、账号、全局三级配置，修改后需重启网关。私聊无需@即可触发，还可通过allowFrom等参数限制特定用户或群组发言。\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fa9b928d2e85acee\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.saiita.com.cn\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"49e433fa4d537af5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n让 AI 住进飞书：OpenClaw 接入飞书机器人的完整实践\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"49e433fa4d537af5\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cnblogs.com/MrVolleyball/p/19676465\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a5e36a423234cf2f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n在上一篇文章成功部署 OpenClaw 之后，接下来我们让 AI 真正\\\"走进工作流\\\"——接入飞书机器人。 本文记录了完整的接入流程，包括飞书应用创建、权限配置、 OpenClaw Feishu 插件启用、Pairing 配对机制以及群聊模式配置。\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a5e36a423234cf2f\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.cnblogs.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bc33128b24f52161\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n团队协作效率翻倍!OpenClaw飞书机器人部署保姆级流程（多智能体+阿里云/本地部署+百炼API配置）\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bc33128b24f52161\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1716839\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7bb08d55111f183e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n\\\"在飞书群里直接喊一声'帮我写段Python代码'，AI就秒回解决方案\\\"——2026年，OpenClaw多智能体与飞书的深度联动，彻底改变了团队协作模式。参考文章精准拆解了\\\"多智能体创建+飞书机器人接入\\\"的核心流程，让每个智能体都能成为飞书群里的\\\"专属助手\\\"，无需@即可直接对话，大幅降低团队 ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"7bb08d55111f183e\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"developer.aliyun.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"55755b878d269035\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nOpenClaw 定时任务cron配置指南：飞书渠道避坑详解_delivering to feishu requires target ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"55755b878d269035\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://blog.csdn.net/k1_maple/article/details/158974913\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f6979e8159b75532\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n八、总结 配置 OpenClaw 飞书定时任务的关键点： 必须指定 --account （和你的飞书账户配置一致） 必须指定 --channel feishu 必须指定 --to （chat:群聊 ID 或 user:用户 OpenID） 时间格式用 ISO 8601 （带时区） 查看日志排查问题 （/tmp/ openclaw /*.log） 按照这个配置，定时任务应该能正常工作了。如果还有问题 ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f6979e8159b75532\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"blog.csdn.net\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"openclaw feishu requireMention 配置 群ID","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":1161,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bd03c3922756d2c3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenClaw 接入飞书 （2）- 群组、权限、多渠道 - 知乎\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bd03c3922756d2c3\">>>","url":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2013958294977394200","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bdb2566423dd37fc\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n上一篇我们聊了 OpenClaw 接入飞书的基础部署流程，从装 CLI 到私聊跑通，顺利的话 20 分钟搞定。 建议先读一下： 《一条命令装好，几步配置跑通—— OpenClaw 飞书部署实战》 但私聊只是起点。真正要在团队里用起来，你一定会遇到这些问题： 怎么让机器人进群？进了群怎么控制谁能跟它说话？ 能不 ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bdb2566423dd37fc\">>>","siteName":"zhuanlan.zhihu.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"87f147124cebbef5\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenClaw 飞书群消息配置：requireMention 详解 - SaiitaのBlog\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"87f147124cebbef5\">>>","url":"https://www.saiita.com.cn/note/computer/ai/openclaw/openclaw-%E9%A3%9E%E4%B9%A6%E7%BE%A4%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%EF%BC%9Arequiremention-%E8%AF%A6%E8%A7%A3.html","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fa9b928d2e85acee\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nrequireMention参数控制群聊中机器人是否需被@才回复：true（默认）时仅响应@消息，false时响应所有消息但会增加API调用量。该参数可在群、账号、全局三级配置，修改后需重启网关。私聊无需@即可触发，还可通过allowFrom等参数限制特定用户或群组发言。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fa9b928d2e85acee\">>>","siteName":"www.saiita.com.cn"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"49e433fa4d537af5\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n让 AI 住进飞书：OpenClaw 接入飞书机器人的完整实践\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"49e433fa4d537af5\">>>","url":"https://www.cnblogs.com/MrVolleyball/p/19676465","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a5e36a423234cf2f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n在上一篇文章成功部署 OpenClaw 之后，接下来我们让 AI 真正\"走进工作流\"——接入飞书机器人。 本文记录了完整的接入流程，包括飞书应用创建、权限配置、 OpenClaw Feishu 插件启用、Pairing 配对机制以及群聊模式配置。\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a5e36a423234cf2f\">>>","siteName":"www.cnblogs.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bc33128b24f52161\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n团队协作效率翻倍!OpenClaw飞书机器人部署保姆级流程（多智能体+阿里云/本地部署+百炼API配置）\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bc33128b24f52161\">>>","url":"https://developer.aliyun.com/article/1716839","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7bb08d55111f183e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n\"在飞书群里直接喊一声'帮我写段Python代码'，AI就秒回解决方案\"——2026年，OpenClaw多智能体与飞书的深度联动，彻底改变了团队协作模式。参考文章精准拆解了\"多智能体创建+飞书机器人接入\"的核心流程，让每个智能体都能成为飞书群里的\"专属助手\"，无需@即可直接对话，大幅降低团队 ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"7bb08d55111f183e\">>>","siteName":"developer.aliyun.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"55755b878d269035\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nOpenClaw 定时任务cron配置指南：飞书渠道避坑详解_delivering to feishu requires target ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"55755b878d269035\">>>","url":"https://blog.csdn.net/k1_maple/article/details/158974913","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f6979e8159b75532\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n八、总结 配置 OpenClaw 飞书定时任务的关键点： 必须指定 --account （和你的飞书账户配置一致） 必须指定 --channel feishu 必须指定 --to （chat:群聊 ID 或 user:用户 OpenID） 时间格式用 ISO 8601 （带时区） 查看日志排查问题 （/tmp/ openclaw /*.log） 按照这个配置，定时任务应该能正常工作了。如果还有问题 ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f6979e8159b75532\">>>","siteName":"blog.csdn.net"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774364366816}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9572480","parentId":"b8df763d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:59:41.272Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found the key information! The saiita.com.cn blog post has exactly what I need:\n\n\"requireMention参数控制群聊中机器人是否需被@才回复：true（默认）时仅响应@消息，false时响应所有消息但会增加API调用量。该参数可在群、账号、全局三级配置，修改后需重启网关。私聊无需@即可触发，还可通过allowFrom等参数限制特定用户或群组发言。\"\n\nAnd from the Aliyun article: \"无需@即可直接对话，大幅降低团队...\"\n\n\nThis is exactly what the user needs. Now I'm formulating the solution: set `requireMention: false` at the group level to allow responses without @mentioning the bot, though there's a trade-off with increased API usage. The group ID from the conversation context is `oc_074cb1631c4e9dfc26e486fd17c7d32c`, and I can configure this either through the config file or via CLI command.","thinkingSignature":"e6778a1fa30be8413d0f16a797b5dc5d0bcbd271df5011c1b517d0af431e633a"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n好消息！**找到了解决方案！** 🎉\n\nOpenClaw 飞书频道支持 `requireMention` 参数，可以针对单个群配置：\n\n**效果：**\n- `requireMention: true`（默认）→ 必须 @ 我才回复\n- `requireMention: false` → 群里所有消息我都能收到并判断是否回复，**不用 @**\n\n**配置方法（在你的 Mac mini 上运行）：**\n\n```bash\n# 针对这个群关闭 @ 限制\nopenclaw config set channels.feishu.groups.oc_074cb1631c4e9dfc26e486fd17c7d32c.requireMention false --strict-json\n\n# 重启网关生效\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**注意：** 关闭后我 会收到群里所有消息，API 调用量会增加一些。另外为了避免抢答/串线，多 Agent 群建议配合\"昵称命中\"规则使用——先 @ 我建立身份，群里其他人也可以通过 @各自的 Agent 来区分。\n\n你要试试这个配置吗？需要我帮你跑命令吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17560,"output":430,"cacheRead":17422,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35412,"cost":{"input":0.005268,"output":0.000516,"cacheRead":0.00104532,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00682932}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774364366823,"responseId":"0611d9cf86c274da2138944864547901"}}
