{"type":"message","id":"1bb4a2c6","parentId":"5d8decec","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:13:49.704Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b115a8cef1d4cb00169c2aa2c8f9481919017321b2faa376b\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 那就行 👍  \n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你检查当前 OpenClaw 配置，确认这个群有没有把 `requireMention` 设成 `false`。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b115a8cef1d4cb00169c2aa2caaf48191a546ea947e755852\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":33899,"output":56,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33955,"cost":{"input":0.0847475,"output":0.00084,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0855875}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774365225793,"responseId":"resp_0b115a8cef1d4cb00169c2aa2a49108191a872fca4d7ff8505"}}
